{"tid":2379203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[爆毒易］有行會成員否認佛系抗疫　有確診者指政府要負很大責任","createTime":"2021-01-25T05:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T05:38:14.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"48c540d13b1ffe4bffc4ba445901f907e9f3128e","tid":2379203,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:38:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572202-20210125.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572202-20210125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABRzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=8f4b4fef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572202-20210125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7859d259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572202-20210125.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新型肺炎疫情持續一年，有確診者接受本台專訪時說，已做盡可以做的防疫衞生措施，仍然受感染，認為政府要負上很大責任。<br />\n<br />\n有安老院舍院友的家屬說，疫情下禁止探訪，形容安排太苛刻。<br />\n<br />\n有行政會議成員說，政府並非「佛系抗疫」，只是無用封城一類極端手法，而是精準微細的策略，應對疫症。"}]}